		"description": "DOCUMENTATION: A use-after-free vulnerability was found in OpenSSL. Calling the OpenSSL API SSL_free_buffers function may cause memory to be accessed that was previously freed in some situations. \n            STATEMENT: The API in question is not used by any application shipped by Red Hat. We also are not aware of any 3rd-party application using this API.",
